   PART III — The standard analytic inputs.  The paper (§2) uses three
   classical facts; A2 (Mertens' third theorem, PART III-A) and A1
   (Dirichlet AP reciprocal divergence, proven above via `A1proof`) are
   now FULLY PROVEN, so only A3 remains as a cited axiom.
